title: Cash Clicker (mobile friendly)
description:
This game is inspired by cookie clicker!

Special thanks to:

@warfame 
@TheBadDev 
@MasterOskarYT
@Fourseen

Bug fixes and updates: 

Beta ver 0.0 Added a coin sprite, and whenever pressed, it would keep a record of how many clicks the player has done.

Beta ver 0.1 'Pop' sound effect added when clicking.

Beta ver 1.0 Added a wave, Cash multiplier, a shop with coin upgrade and coin per second counter.

Beta ver 2.0 Added smooth animations for most sprite and sound effects.

Beta ver 2.1 Fixed a bug where the cps counter would not count the coin upgrade.

Beta ver 2.2 Added settings.

Beta ver 2.3 Added a cloud variable for the 'RICHEST'

Beta ver 2.4 fixed bug where Cps doesn't count the multiplier.

Beta ver 3.0 Added auto-clicker upgrade (in 'shop' menu), changed the layout, costume cash counter and cash/s counter, changed cog (settings) icon, fixed bug for the multiplier to count the upgrades and added backdrop clone coins (shown whenever clicking).

Beta ver 3.1 fixed bug where 'cps'(in settings) and cash/s won't count the auto clicks.

Beta ver 3.2 fixed a mistake where 'cash/s' was counting the wrong variable. (made my brain hurt!!!), fixed bug where the wave would get stuck in one place if clicking or idling for too long and brightened the backdrop coin clones.

Beta ver 3.3 fixed a mistake where 'Richest' variable would not show. (didn't notice when creating the 'settings' code). 

(Full release) Ver 1.0 changed the wave to rise when the clicks per sec are above 1 not cash per sec, added pages system in the shop menu and added cash bot, now shows cash/s for upgrades in the shop menu and cleaned unnecessary codes.

Ver 1.1 changed the gameplay balance.

Ver 1.2 changed 'multiplier' code to fit the cookie clicker and based the wave on the multiplier.

Ver 1.3 Added intro, new soundtrack, new auto-clickers and added missing sound effects.

Ver 1.4 fixed bug where the shop pages variable counter would show '1111' 

Ver 2.0 added rush mode! rush models and rush multiplier.

Ver 2.1 updated rush coin look, changed the speed of the rush coin, fixed bug where the rush multiplier would appear outside of the screen and fixed bug where the rush multiplier would only show 'x10'.

Ver 2.2 (thanks to @TheBadDev) Bug fixed where if pressing the shop button more then once, the shop menu won't display properly.

Ver 2.3 bug fixed when rush mode active, the multiplier stays at 'x50' instead of changing and gave the 'settings' icon a hitbox.

Ver 2.4 Added 4 new auto-clickers!!! Changed the backdrop to a gradient and fixed bug where the rush coin won't spawn but the alert sound is played.

Ver 2.5 Added small touches to backdrop coin clones and rush coins to rotate and move down at different speeds and updated the thumbnail.

Ver 2.6 (thanks to @MasterOskarYT) Fixed a bug which caused the whole game to become laggy and unresponsive especially the clones. (caused by the clones from the cash counter and cash per sec counter). 

Ver 2.7 (thanks to @Fourseen) Changed gameplay balance so that you must buy the previous upgrade to unlock the upgrade before it, cleaned up code and sprites and enhanced effects.

title: Cash clicker
description:
It's so addicting!!! WARNING MOST THINGS YOU CAN BUY HAVE A CERTAIN PLACE YOU CLICK ON THEM SO YOU WILL JUST HAVE TO FIND THEM!:) Post what u got in the comments! I added global high score (it resets if it gets to high)! If you put to much in the auto tbuyer even if you run out of money after you get more money it will buy more until it gives you the amount you wanted. THERE ARE EASTER EGGS!!!!!!!
ACHIEVEMENTS --> striking rich$$$! get 100,000 money. Hollywood get 3 or more celebrities.
instructions: Click on the big coin to get money. Click on anything with a cost UNDER IT to buy it (you need enough money). Press s to see how many of everything you have and press h to hide it. Press m to play music and press n to stop the music. Click on the star to show achievements and click again to hide achievements. When Money Monsters face (aka cookie monsters face) comes up click on it to get 60 money! when you are robbed you lose 50 to 100 money and the words robbed will come up on the coin for 2 seconds.Click on the bank (it has a thing under it telling you how much is in the bank) and it will ask you if you want to give or take then how much. Click on the auto buyer (AB in a red circle) and it will ask you how many of it you want to buy (so you don't have to click the words like 1,000 times):).

title: Cash Clicker!
description:
Enjoy! Leave a like and fav if you would like to. Tell me anything in the comments about bugs, improvements, etc. This would really help me make stuff you guys like!

instructions:
Click the coin to get money. There's a shop to buy auto-clickers. Buy the best auto-clicker in the world to access the next one! Buy clicker upgrades to get more money per click! And at last, enjoy swimming in that money!

This game is pretty much fully developed. There may be a few updates, however, I doubt I may work on this in the near future. I will likely work on other games, though.
